Developer Terms of Use
des:
Wall Street Time Traveler allows players to travel back to a random date in the past where they will be presented with investment options and their prices on that date.

After selecting investments players will travel back to present day to view their profits ( or losses ) and their score will be calculated.

A player's score will be calculated relative to the range of potential profits during that period so that it accurately reflects players who made the best investment decisions, even during a time period where there are few ( or zero ) profitable investments.

Players can upgrade to Premium Edition for additional features including Story Mode where players can become a fugitive on the run from a time traveling task force, the ability to compete with other players on our global leaderboards and more!

Disclaimers: 
This skill can only be accessed on a device with a screen.
